tab = pd.crosstab(data['CUISINE DESCRIPTION'], data['GRADE'])
specs = {'size': 40}
grade_by_cuisine = tab.plot(kind='barh', stacked=False, figsize=(20,80), fontsize=22)
grade_by_cuisine.set_xlabel("Cuisine", fontdict=specs)

specs = {'size': 32}
totals = tab.sum(1)

    tab2[tab.columns[j]] = tab.iloc[:,j]/totals
